{"tid":1829100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【華為危機】禁用Android、Google Maps 改與荷蘭TomTom地圖合作","createTime":"2020-01-18T12:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T12:42:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3324082513ca0f2d9c346ceb654fd1239a04b306","tid":1829100,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200118/UNOGBRQOQD7SJSRPEWXKZZCWLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200118%2FUNOGBRQOQD7SJSRPEWXKZZCWLA%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=a3fcbd9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200118%2FUNOGBRQOQD7SJSRPEWXKZZCWLA%2F&h=c6023d2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200118/UNOGBRQOQD7SJSRPEWXKZZCWLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【華為危機】禁用Android、Google Maps 改與荷蘭TomTom地圖合作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200118/large/1579334572_c8ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200118%2Flarge%2F1579334572_c8ce.jpg&h=1767acd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為與TomTom合作。<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n美國特朗普政府去年基於安全考慮，將華為列入黑名單，導致國產手機華為禁止在新發行手機使用Android作業系統，以及Google地圖（Google Maps）等熱間應用程式，需要自行研發手機操作系統。華為為了填補不足，與荷蘭導航與數位地圖公司TomTom合作，今日（18日）宣佈，華為在智能手機軟體上可使用TomTom地圖與服務。<br />\n<br />\n華為與TomTom的協議已敲定，代表華為現在可以使用Tom Tom的地圖、交通資訊與導航軟體，以研發智能手機App。TomTom發言人梅斯特拉（Remco Meerstra）表示，這項協議是在前一段時間達成，但TomTom一直未有公佈。梅斯特拉不願提供關於協議的進一步細節。<br />\n<br />\n中央社<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【78頁電子書●你不能不知的毛澤東】<br />\n老毛秘史和他的女人們 熟讀紅色抗爭策略<br />\n一按即睇︰ <a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/e/fJX5EvX1v2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2Fe%2FfJX5EvX1v2&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1BnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=18aaea90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/e/fJX5EvX1v2</a><br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【匿名港警爆大鑊】<br />\n韓國KBS時事節目《時事直擊：香港 被自殺》<br />\n一按即睇"},{"pid":"f2f3d6d381d2f67ed9a5567ee3c794ab5aad5bbb","tid":1829100,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祗要有番1月1號維園草地個人數量，<br />\n必定可以逼爆起行。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家一定要 準時準時準時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這才是<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">【全球8國15市聯手，1.19 天下制裁大遊行！】</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826839</a></blockquote>坐爆唔起行嘅話，<br />\n必定繼續會逼爆中環畢打街同德輔道中（電車路）<br />\n<br />\n1月1號被強制腰斬， <br />\n再出過嚟顯示畀世界睇 <span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人嘅不屈同超強既韌力</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅</span>"},{"pid":"898822e8c92c13cf751dffea1ea7a6a809354290","tid":1829100,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVegVOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVegVOu.jpg&h=a144f866&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7877f9d52c7d286fa6ae6377df46ab977bbc8b98","tid":1829100,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"大家千其唔好由中環遊行至銅記 但Shopping 行街路線可自決<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1829112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1829112</a>"}]}